---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="GymForge | About Us" description="Learn more about GymForge, your free fitness toolkit for heavy lifting.">
  <section class="px-4 sm:px-8 py-24 max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full flex-grow flex flex-col">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-gym-muted">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-accent-lime transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-white">About</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-5xl text-white tracking-tight">
        About GymForge<span class="text-accent-lime">.</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gym-muted leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-6">
      <p>
        GymForge is a free, high-performance fitness toolkit designed for powerlifters, bodybuilders, and anyone serious about their strength training. We believe that professional-grade tools should be accessible to everyone without the bloat of sign-ups, subscriptions, or intrusive data collection.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to provide clean, accurate, and easy-to-use calculators that help you optimize your training, track your progress, and push your limits. From calculating the perfect plate load to estimating your one-rep max, GymForge is built to be your digital companion on the gym floor.
      </p>
      <p>
        Built with modern web technologies, GymForge is optimized for speed and reliability, ensuring you get the answers you need as quickly as possible so you can get back to your sets.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
